Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没问过他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我已经知道了 他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫高桥七美 开学的第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果可以交很多朋友就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...我是高桥七美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请...请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是山本有里 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请...请问 你初中在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旭中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以和你们一起去上课的教室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是坐在最前排的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我叫高桥七美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是西中的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.09,0:02:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班级好像没有旭中的女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在我旁边的山本好像就是旭中的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打听了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于元晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴啊 我曾经和他参加同一个冬季补习班
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得超帅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是在女生还是男生中 都很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他们班三分之二的女生初中三年内都至少喜欢过他一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班级 居然有这样的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 山本和一个叫矢野的同学是同一所学校的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说三分之二的女生都喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 你做班干部吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做比较轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和元晴做同样的干部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是候选选举方式呢 还是指名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过成为候选人 会不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我来推荐你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 名字是什么来着?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水...水...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...嗯...嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问不出口...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 那个女生叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水...水...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没问过他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我已经知道了 他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野元晴 你来做班长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指名的方式太蛮横了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有候选人 也没人推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我来当候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副班长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是副班长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...我想推荐一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先想推荐...水原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是把水口错记成水原了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 变成我当班长了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}下面宣布一下班委的职务和班级目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起忘记别人名字的家伙 谁比较失礼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忘记了别人名字的我不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 矢野有没有女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听说他和很多女人交往过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比自己大的和比自己小的都有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 只是据说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去问问山本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我貌似是剩下的那三分之一的女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙 我不清楚 没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有想的那么有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 升学志向讨论完毕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也参加社团活动好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升学志向讨论花了多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7分钟?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只有5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的 15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被你这种人说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想你可能没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对 我没有心跳加速 只是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没有想到他会那样对我开口说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数1完全不懂 心里很着急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的升学志向是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私大文科
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就不要读理科了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把看理科的精力放到学习文科上才更有效些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 太差的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差的话也只能这个样子了 再怎么学都不会有效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把精力浪费在不喜欢的事上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下下周是去远足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那之前有考试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 都没有好好学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.43,0:07:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 你有把握吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 应该说已经放弃了 数1可能会得0分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会0分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 真的得了0分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快决定远足的工作分配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作分配吗 好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采购的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 采购的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很麻烦 让女生去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵子 我身体不好 所以呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直不坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西还是女生比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 为什么麻烦的事总要推给我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害啊 高桥的数学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被骗了 不要被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙露出那种笑容 只是因为我数学不及格罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开红灯可是不能升级的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是山本不是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的志向是读文科的话 把数学扔掉也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是亮红灯可是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦心情不好的时候 我就会来到这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\1c&H6A00D5&\move(420,450,370,390)}怦怦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怦怦什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,87分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这不是值得在意的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 人总有擅长和不擅长的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力在擅长的事上下功夫就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 0分在某些意义上说 也挺厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你有不擅长的事么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的有的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太受女生欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 你有没有其他的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太引人注目 很快就会被人看上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很麻烦 但很快就会被选为班委
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有讨厌的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水性杨花的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5个 耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是哪个都不是烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水性杨花的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你不要看不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样 其实我非常专一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 会喜欢什么样的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上了什么样的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果交往的人水性杨花 你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我想要知道这些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会说这种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有什么烦恼的话 我会倾听的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且刚才你也听了我的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那样阳光的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 难道想和矢野一起 深深地...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 对矢野 很喜...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦恼之类的 是活着的人的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的我 还不能理解矢野这句话的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那个 徒步远足的注意事项
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家先乘巴士到出发地点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行程一共42km
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去说一下注意事项
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止使用手机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止途中购物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 倾心于这个超过分男生的我 真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:12:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手机集中过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没带呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没带?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说嘛 这次忘记带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道矢野真的没带手机?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,42km走得完吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想和矢野一起吃午饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七 你去打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们是正副班长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以...一起吃午饭吗 山本...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把山本叫来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不可以 但是和她很难讲上话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:13:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这么说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 但你要把矢野叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌那家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把矢野叫过来 山本会不高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么人讨厌矢野 为什么山本会讨厌他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说中学和他一个班级的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在好像也经常在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到中点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝42km出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午...午饭 和大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行是行 不过你们跟的上我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得越来越累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色也一直都不变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经厌烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在20km的地方返回就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多可以吃午饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 最终还是没跟上他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要紧吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝水吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让老师用车送回去?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师应该在20km处的洋房吃午饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概还要1-2个小时才能过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1-2个小时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之如果遇到有手机的人 我会帮你告诉老师的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本 水果可以吃吗 吃了可能会好点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带来了榨的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢 休息之后还不能恢复么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能等老师来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 我虽说是负责人 却一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 有谁回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内和我联系过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有吃早饭?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有脱水症状?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有补充盐分?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 那怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好等车子来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么和老师联系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 现在在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25km处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达终点还要花多长时间?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2小时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师他们还没通过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人 把手机藏哪里带来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到中点去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中点?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们现在在露营地的烤肉店吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子5分钟就能到这 你们陪着她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有带手机的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没带 不是被拿走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你们呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能管理好自己的手机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带着 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 你等在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.56,0:17:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好歹我也是负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是拖我后腿 我就丢下你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手机号 没有变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学是一个班级的 所以知道号码
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么慢吞吞的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要丢下你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是没用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候 比起山本的身体更加担心别的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学的时候 你和山本关系好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 基本上没说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前就不怎么讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 以前就是这样的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪样的感觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎么表达自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是独生女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是独生女 她曾有个姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 曾?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为她去年夏天死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道不是更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像讨厌被人同情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么去世了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 参加了葬礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有这样的经历 所以也不大明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是很难过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.76,0:18:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我很不懂得体谅别人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在说这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为矢野在身边 心中一直怦怦跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像发烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,25km的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么老师 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我没喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有我们能做的事 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后只要在这等着就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一盘五花肉 然后再来2杯乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一个烤牛舌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 还好矢野来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢...谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样无邪地笑着的人 我从来没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢 你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本被老师开车送回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家确认后上车 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚才和他分开 现在又想见他了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才谢谢你了 帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来车子来了 把山本送回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很关心朋友 真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 毕竟发生了很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她去年夏天死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的话肯定无法振作起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围还没有人去世 所以我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么感受呢 会一蹶不振么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然觉得她不是这类人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只看人的外表是不会了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 这样很危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也没有见他哭过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果哭过 失去理智的话 还能够理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那家伙是还在哀伤呢 或者已经看开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许两者都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不了解他 我觉得他很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:22:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会可怕呢 我觉得她是个内心坚强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我还是觉得他在我面前表现的脆弱一点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这样子我会很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内和她那么要好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在不同班级 我们还是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说谁的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.54,0:22:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒得脱了皮 很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.51,0:22:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然对女孩子说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 好恐怖的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.21,0:22:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.74,0:22:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是表现出厚颜无耻 得意忘形的嘴脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这家伙真是一点办法都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我 非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山本的姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.59,0:23:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她去年夏天死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是矢野的...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.91,0:25:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.04,0:25:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.88,0:25:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.96,0:25:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的喜欢我?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.32,0:25:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.21,0:25:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这种喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.19,0:25:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你是不是真的真的喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.81,0:25:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.52,0:25:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.36,0:25:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女朋友是臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.73,0:25:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和男人在一起 发生事故的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.45,0:25:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她前男友
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.00,0:25:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本没有分手

